{"tid":94724,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"呢舊野到底係有咩用? 拎出去賣唔賣到錢?","createTime":"2017-01-25T12:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T17:02:40.000Z","uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4152f7cbb2f461c491193ebab66fdb92a2a6a2bd","tid":94724,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"7,8年買廠機比我<br />\n唔知乜鳩黎<br />\n我唔明點解電腦要過左呢舊野再去喇叭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我直接插咪又聽到<br />\n舊野仲要用電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac89091de8eb5bf9750314d07d471ea8afab548","tid":94724,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"唔記得補圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PyD63PT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyD63PT.jpg&h=9c948188&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35b77974aa06159418356df9018ffc5d3c52d9c9","tid":94724,"uid":71114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"Made in China"},{"pid":"c8b4f3fd5e8fdecb59e8da1641f5d674ea6897f0","tid":94724,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"BOOM~~"},{"pid":"39a79cb262510a48e686effe99e7d884794bb427","tid":94724,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"冇人知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75702a3ce76c5d0251cc60a56afeef3922068aee","tid":94724,"uid":7024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:20:59.000Z","msg":"呢舊野應該係低音箱黎"},{"pid":"54d5bbde2a3ea0f3ccd3a72592268fd6942944b5","tid":94724,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢舊野應該係低音箱黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎出深水埗值唔值錢"},{"pid":"5eff43189f183335c2e682033d1faa35ab3bac49","tid":94724,"uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢舊野應該係低音箱黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎出深水埗值唔值錢</blockquote><br />\n都賣到錢架<br />\n10蚊應該無走雞，有無20蚊睇你牙力"},{"pid":"00430c1450b78cf8279fc7e1ec501d8f216dd845","tid":94724,"uid":68446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"竟然有人唔知subwoofer有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你對speaker負責出高音，個driver因為唔夠大所以出唔到好低音，呢個subwoofer就負責嗰part<br />\n仲有佢插電就可以做埋amplifer推你對細野"},{"pid":"de9d7f93e3700536535ae86adc3f24b1a245ffbd","tid":94724,"uid":7024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢舊野應該係低音箱黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎出深水埗值唔值錢</blockquote><br />\n你俾返錢人幫你掉件垃圾就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc09e99cdfe4a64047e02a83f89da21adf8d5fa","tid":94724,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係好似得你唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05682cec90591772b650cd71a5128f63e8761bbb","tid":94724,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然有人唔知subwoofer有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你對speaker負責出高音，個driver因為唔夠大所以出唔到好低音，呢個subwoofer就負責嗰part<br />\n仲有佢插電就可以做埋amplifer推你對細野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔關driver事，關你對細喇叭事<br />\n每個喇叭都負責唔同嘅音（簡單啲高中低），又因為結構問題，唔會有喇叭做哂高中低音<br />\n如你幅圖，subwoofer負責低音，細喇叭就中、高音，你可以bypass唔用subwoofer, 但就唔建議，因為你張soundcard/chips輸出有限，用番佢個subwoofer推就夠啦<br />\n<br />\n值唔值錢？俾錢人地都未必黎收"},{"pid":"ebdd99101be16a84153b8337a5fe15ca7f919013","tid":94724,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打們的解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用左幾年耳筒所以唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0903ee1429c9b02bdf2b50562f5fa6ee1f1cee","tid":94724,"uid":68446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔關driver事，關你對細喇叭事</blockquote><br />\n其實我係指speaker driver姐係個喇叭單元，唔係software driver<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sor，搞到有混淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a1fe33d52326a220d69b1c03ffd661458446f5","tid":94724,"uid":1314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"幾多歲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}